I bled for Sagan, that means I went on a baguette starvation diet! Yes, no baguettes for 100 days. Sure I ate everything else. I am proud to announce that I am the newest member of the @sako7squad and a SaKO7 ambassador. My question to you is do you have what it takes to be a SaKO7 ambassador??? They are looking for credible creators, ambassadors and influencers to fly the SaKO7 flag! If you think you have what it takes. Send @sako7official a DM and your various social media pages.
